TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
What is all this fighting about?
Do you know anything about cults in the city?
Text: 도시의 사교에 대해 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Do you know of any work I might find?
You know where me finds work?
Text: 너 나 일 찾을 곳 알아?

TextEng: Do you know anything else about it?
Text: 그것에 대해 더 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Can you tell me about Luskan?
Text: 러스칸에 대해 말해 줄 수 있어?

TextEng: I want to ask you something else.
You're one of the brothel girls, then?
Text: 그럼 넌 매춘굴 여자 중 하나구나?

TextEng: How is it the brothel is still open?
Let me ask you something else.
